      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable vehicle that gets the job done? This car is in honest, fair condition and has been a reliable part of our daily routine. While it shows some expected signs of wear and tear both inside and out, it still runs steadily and is ready for many more miles. It\u2019s the perfect choice for someone looking for functional transportation at a great value!",
