      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and has served as a reliable daily driver, though it clearly shows its age and mileage. The exterior paint has lost some of its original luster and features several visible scratches and minor dings consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin shows noticeable wear on the upholstery and carpets, though all essential features remain functional. While the car runs and drives well, it is being sold as-is, and buyers should expect some upcoming maintenance requirements typical for a vehicle in this state. It remains a solid option for anyone needing a functional, budget-friendly vehicle.",
