      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved by a dedicated enthusiast. The exterior features a flawless, mirror-like finish with absolutely no stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. The alloy wheels are pristine with zero curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with deep tread. Inside, the cabin is a 'time capsule'\u2014the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, free from any creases or wear, and the interior still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every single electronic feature, from the premium sound system to the climate control, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach; it has a documented, full-service history exclusively through authorized dealerships and has been stored in a climate-controlled garage under a soft cover. Never driven in rain or snow, this vehicle looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
